this event that at one point,

00:01:33.100 --> 00:01:35.240
the name considered
was "East Side Story."

00:01:35.240 --> 00:01:37.840
And what a different production
that might have been.

00:01:37.840 --> 00:01:41.630
Maybe Jamie and Clive will
tell us more about that.

00:01:41.630 --> 00:01:45.100
So Google's inviting
audiences to dive

00:01:45.100 --> 00:01:47.260
into the history and legacy
of the musical theater

00:01:47.260 --> 00:01:49.150
masterpiece online.

00:01:49.150 --> 00:01:51.370
